assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Toyo Machinery & Metal Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells plastic injection molding machines, die-casting machines, peripheral automation equipment, and related components worldwide. The company offers electric injection molding machines, two-color/dissimilar-material injection molding machines, electric vertical injection molding machines, optical disc molding machines, and super precision molding systems. Its die-casting machines include electric servo control die-casting machines, electric servo-driven die-casting machines, and hydraulic die-casting machines with multi-injection systems. The company was formerly known as Bouki Seizo Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Toyo Machinery & Metal Co., Ltd. in January 1962. Toyo Machinery & Metal Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1925 and is headquartered in Akashi, Japan.
